{"tid":1801740,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［心灰意冷］女朋友係港豬，你問我答","createTime":"2019-12-29T00:47:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T04:15:49.000Z","uid":316967,"like":11,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"b7f5d83016b12a9f72e54464d6db140e353cff69","tid":1801740,"uid":316967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T00:47:47.000Z","msg":"其實冇乜好問<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對身邊所有野都唔關心<br />\n只關心玩得開唔開心<br />\n由6月到而加都乜都唔去理<br />\n我已經成日同佢講黑警啲仆街野，同佢解釋成個反送中運動，但佢只係聽完就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢走去食藍店，我話唔撚食，佢屌9我話食飯都要分藍黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我發夢佢又係咁叫我唔好去，叫我留係屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小弟垃圾，想講分手但開唔到口<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唔係接受唔到唔同政見，但今次唔係政唔政見既問題，而係良知既問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呻完，幫手推下行動po，唔該"},{"pid":"46331e884175dabdfc6960e4a2606b216268512a","tid":1801740,"uid":80851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T00:51:08.000Z","msg":"你地幾大"},{"pid":"42a48213e2178552d090a70fd7f7900d23b8e172","tid":1801740,"uid":321674,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T00:54:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"952e76b654074e3360f470266b5072fd28b98125","tid":1801740,"uid":196924,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"42a48213e2178552d090a70fd7f7900d23b8e172","tid":1801740,"uid":321674,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T00:54:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T01:00:42.000Z","msg":"咁你都要，block"},{"pid":"6bd9feb6068d21c6f26c8388118fec155b862725","tid":1801740,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T01:08:41.000Z","msg":"新移民？，"},{"pid":"0a9ef38e99ad34a089f1216da1b09c3cef56a2aa","tid":1801740,"uid":147952,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"